Titolo: Gangster Town

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Gangster Town is a light gun game developed for the Master System that was released in 1987. It is set in a great American city overtaken with crime during the 1920s. You are an FBI agent armed with a machine gun and courage. Your goal is to rid the town of thugs.The game supports use of the Sega Light Phaser. Two light guns can be used simultaneously to provide co-operative play in two player mode.